Match Solitaire PrivacyÂ Policy
Personal Information
Match Solitaire does not not collect, store or share any personal information or location data, except as specified below.
Analytics
Match Solitaire uses standard analytics tools to receive anonymous usage statistics in order to facilitate bug fixes and improve the product.
Advertising and 3rd Parties
Match Solitaire uses a third party to market, sell, and display advertisements that you may see when you play the game and
			may place a unique 'cookie' on your computer or mobile device. 
			More information can be found at
https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads
.
Questions
This privacy policy applies to all versions of Match Solitaire offered by Hot Chai Productions, LLC. If you have any questions about this policy, please feel free to
contact us through our website
